{"tid":1590483,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中學生嘅麻煩入一入嚟，學校升旗禮-願榮光歸香港","createTime":"2019-09-23T17:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T17:37:13.000Z","uid":231562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8cdcb154793f414bcf37979ddb820a7a31bd2d45","tid":1590483,"uid":231562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"我唔知你哋學校星期禮係幾多號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係麻煩你哋嗰日同我大大聲唱國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戴口罩full gear<br />\n有咁大聲唱咁大聲，唔要聽到有黨歌聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果學校啲人好港豬做唔到嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔該覺醒嘅同學做好自己本分<br />\n要俾老師睇到你地嘅決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"f03ffb0f1b1ece5a207f54b6da9983b73505a4b8","tid":1590483,"uid":231562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:35:42.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"de8c36974c1fdcb26eddc56ca88d011986940ebf","tid":1590483,"uid":231562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:35:52.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"ab9f55ac47c2b423bc1d7e776b8fd0c2c3aff5e7","tid":1590483,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"5d4b767764617c8053b7b258a4b390a6959447b1","tid":1590483,"uid":231562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:36:03.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"c581477a88fd974cde90d068b6d04b8c9630d066","tid":1590483,"uid":231562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:36:13.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid"